{"words":[{"word":"knight","count":6},{"word":"painter","count":5},{"word":"underling","count":5},{"word":"cuddle","count":4},{"word":"wuddle","count":4},{"word":"playername","count":3},{"word":"role","count":2},{"word":"plays","count":2},{"word":"night","count":2},{"word":"reveries","count":2},{"word":"villain","count":2},{"word":"giant","count":2},{"word":"crazed","count":2},{"word":"echoes","count":2},{"word":"felled","count":2},{"word":"cheers","count":2},{"word":"day","count":2},{"word":"play","count":2},{"word":"hero","count":2},{"word":"graffiti","count":1},{"word":"chalulu","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"meet","count":1},{"word":"usual","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"imagine","count":1},{"word":"glad","count":1},{"word":"agree","count":1},{"word":"classic","count":1},{"word":"story","count":1},{"word":"turns","count":1},{"word":"giant's","count":1},{"word":"lucky","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"catch","count":1},{"word":"glimpse","count":1},{"word":"valiant","count":1},{"word":"evil","count":1},{"word":"cunning","count":1},{"word":"played","count":1},{"word":"part","count":1},{"word":"vividly","count":1},{"word":"felt","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"eventually","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"dawn","count":1},{"word":"broke","count":1},{"word":"cursed","count":1},{"word":"escorted","count":1},{"word":"town","count":1},{"word":"shadowed","count":1},{"word":"corner","count":1},{"word":"slowly","count":1},{"word":"rose","count":1},{"word":"fumbling","count":1},{"word":"remove","count":1},{"word":"simple","count":1},{"word":"costume","count":1},{"word":"beneath","count":1},{"word":"minion","count":1},{"word":"large","count":1},{"word":"lonely","count":1},{"word":"tireless","count":1},{"word":"practice","count":1},{"word":"mastered","count":1},{"word":"convincingly","count":1},{"word":"mad","count":1},{"word":"fooled","count":1},{"word":"believing","count":1},{"word":"faced","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"however","count":1},{"word":"flowers","count":1},{"word":"applause","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"meant","count":1},{"word":"villains","count":1},{"word":"cheer","count":1},{"word":"troubled","count":1},{"word":"thoughts","count":1},{"word":"picked","count":1},{"word":"brush","count":1},{"word":"painted","count":1},{"word":"feelings","count":1},{"word":"desire","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"reflection","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"deeper","count":1},{"word":"truly","count":1},{"word":"wants","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"heartfelt","count":1},{"word":"performance","count":1},{"word":"brilliant","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"dear","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"That's all the graffiti Chalulu wanted you to see. Let's meet at the usual place, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"What kind of role do you imagine Painter plays in the \"Night Reveries\"?","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"Glad we agree on that. Painter here is the classic villain in this story.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"Turns out the Cuddle Wuddle that plays the giant's underling is Painter himself...","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"Well… I was lucky enough to catch a glimpse of the \"Night Reveries.\"","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"A valiant knight, an evil giant, and a crazed, cunning underling. The Echoes played their part so vividly. It all felt real.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"Eventually, as the first light of dawn broke, the knight felled the giant and his cursed underling. The Echoes then escorted the knight out of the town in cheers.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"But in a shadowed corner, the \"felled\" underling slowly rose, fumbling to remove his simple costume. Beneath it was no crazed minion—just a large, lonely Cuddle Wuddle.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"Through tireless practice, day in and day out, Painter mastered the role of the villain, so convincingly that even the Mad Knight was fooled, believing he faced the true underling.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"However, flowers, applause, and cheers... are never meant for those who play the villains.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"\"If I could be the knight, the hero, would they cheer for me, too?\"","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"Troubled by these thoughts, the Cuddle Wuddle picked up a brush and painted his feelings.","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"The desire to play the knight and become the hero is but a reflection of something deeper. So, tell me, {PlayerName}, what do you think the Cuddle Wuddle truly wants?","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"And maybe a heartfelt \"Your performance was brilliant.\"","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000},{"text":"{PlayerName}, would you help me find our dear Painter?","quest_name":"The Best Audience","quest_id":147900000}]}